name: minnesota-school-district-and-attendance-boundaries-sy2012-2013
notes: This file represents the boundaries of all public school districts and school attendance areas in the state of Minnesota for school year 2012-2013. Each year Minnesota school districts report any changes to their elementary, middle and high school attendance area boundaries. This file was developed from this annual information.
